description:
Non-material amendments to planning permission ref: P2017/3081/FUL dated: 15/01/2019 for the extension to the existing building, including an additional storey above existing building and part 4/ part 5-storey extension over car park, to provide office, workshop, and studio space with an ancillary cafe, together with hard and soft landscaping.  The applicant seeks to amend Condition 2 (Approved drawings) to allow for: 
-	External changes to the landscaped area outside of the western extension as well as the visitor cycle location near to the bus stop location;
-	Introduction of a small solid upstand on the western and southern elevations, and a deeper spandrel on all roof extension elevations.
-	Amendments to the entrance and reception levels to create an improved escape route;
-	Relocation of the lift core;  
-	Improvements to the accessible WC facilities;
-	Updated door arrangement on the fifth floor; 
-	Removal of access stairs and flue at roof level and the addition of other low-level roof kit.
